stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Start
    Start --> Handshake: initiate

    Handshake --> Active: accepted
    Handshake --> Closed: rejected

    Active --> RFP_Sent: send_rfp

    RFP_Sent --> Proposal_Received: proposal_received
    RFP_Sent --> Closed: timeout

    Proposal_Received --> Negotiating: counter_proposal
    Proposal_Received --> Settling: accept
    Proposal_Received --> Closed: reject

    Negotiating --> Negotiating: counter_proposal
    Negotiating --> Settling: accept
    Negotiating --> Closed: reject
    Negotiating --> Escalated: escalate
    Negotiating --> Closed: max_rounds_exceeded

    Escalated --> Negotiating: resume
    Escalated --> Settling: accept
    Escalated --> Closed: reject

    Settling --> Settled: settlement_confirmed
    Settling --> Closed: settlement_failed

    Settled --> [*]
    Closed --> [*]
